title: The House of Rothschild (1934)
description:
From IMDb:
The story of the rise of the Rothschild financial empire founded by Mayer Rothschild and continued by his five sons. From humble beginnings the business grows and helps to finance the war against Napoleon, but it's not always easy, especially because of the predjudices against the family.
Stars: Boris Karloff, Loretta Young and Robert Young
